{"tid":1234260,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"講真其實我哋冇可能對抗到港共政權","createTime":"2019-06-17T01:21:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-17T02:56:33.000Z","uid":26013,"like":30,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"cd8dc5710a5d676c02f35d6c7b062619b15160b6","tid":1234260,"uid":26013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T01:21:07.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">如果我哋再分化，再散播消極，係一定唔會成功</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n上個post<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1233723/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1233723/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n唔好再散播負面消極<br />\n有好多人唔知頭唔知路比啲三毛帶咗風向<br />\n諗下我哋有幾百萬人<br />\n就算係美國政府遇到咁多人都會驚<br />\n使驚垃圾香港政府咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n人哋宜家係轉玩法<br />\n特首出嚟SAY SOR 玩拖字訣<br />\n警犬出嚟扮好人勸大家<br />\n三毛軍就上各大平台打散你哋<br />\n<br />\n呢個係佢哋唯一可以做嘅嘢<br />\n佢哋得返呢條路<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以我哋想成功就一定要緊守信念<br />\n記住我哋要求咩<br />\n和平派 勇武派各自做自己嘅事 唔好屌人 唔好割蓆<br />\n大家一齊合作先係人民最大嘅力量<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a9d6bad8bf33cb38751ff5975a84e68bc27bd83","tid":1234260,"uid":26013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T01:23:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56b501f3f81b4ab119ec33e14421251ee6861eb3","tid":1234260,"uid":26013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T01:24:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"667aee4a770e505ff1c25ed7409ea9b2ab0606f0","tid":1234260,"uid":39752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T01:25:13.000Z","msg":"香港就嚟輸，想贏就要有下一步<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1234257\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1234257</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"